net.sourceforge.fastupload

Class MemoryUploadParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sourceforge.fastupload.UploadParser
      • net.sourceforge.fastupload.MemoryUploadParser

  • public class MemoryUploadParser
extends UploadParser
    Concrete class of UploadParser that implements main parseList() function that return List<MultiPart> The class read all bytes from ServletInputStream before parse it, which behavior is not as same as StreamUploadParser
    Since:
    0.5.1
    Author:
    Link Qian
